WEBVTT

00:10.646 --> 00:12.229
Morning, Francis.

00:13.231 --> 00:14.865
Is it?

00:14.867 --> 00:16.283
Where are you going?

00:16.285 --> 00:17.618
What, you think I got
nothing better to do

00:17.620 --> 00:19.070
than to sit around here all day?

00:19.072 --> 00:22.690
I'm having lunch at
Sartello's with Tim Kincaid.

00:22.692 --> 00:24.525
He didn't get enough of you
when he was mayor?

00:24.527 --> 00:25.693
I remind him of the glory days.

00:25.695 --> 00:27.211
Well, when Mayor Poole
leaves office,

00:27.213 --> 00:29.296
I'll be the last one
he wants to have lunch with.

00:29.298 --> 00:31.198
Well, I tell better jokes
than you do.

00:31.200 --> 00:32.700
Here, take my
Sartello's card.

00:32.702 --> 00:33.801
No, thanks.

00:33.803 --> 00:35.302
Sartello's is cash only.

00:35.304 --> 00:36.303
I know that.

00:36.305 --> 00:37.972
And I got it.

00:42.260 --> 00:43.877
Okay.

00:45.430 --> 00:47.014
<i>This massage parlor--</i>

00:47.016 --> 00:49.150
it's a legit place of business?

00:49.152 --> 00:51.051
As far as I know.
Uh-huh.

00:51.053 --> 00:52.820
How's the vic?

00:52.822 --> 00:54.221
Not likely.

00:54.223 --> 00:55.373
Uh, where'd they take him?

00:55.375 --> 00:56.323
St. Victor's.

00:56.325 --> 00:59.160
Okay, so we got
three shots fired,

00:59.162 --> 01:00.861
but you only got
two shell casings.

01:00.863 --> 01:02.062
Where's the third?

01:09.287 --> 01:10.421
Hey, well, what do
you know--

01:10.423 --> 01:12.506
there's a third
shell casing.

01:12.508 --> 01:15.092
Make sure you get that.
Any witnesses?

01:15.094 --> 01:17.545
Just the lady
your partner's talking to.

01:17.547 --> 01:19.213
Good. Thanks.

01:20.382 --> 01:22.216
Did you get a look
at the shooter?

01:24.587 --> 01:25.770
No.

01:25.772 --> 01:27.921
Can you describe
what he was wearing?

