01:40.152 --> 01:41.235
She doesn't know.

01:41.237 --> 01:43.904
What else did she say?

01:43.906 --> 01:45.439
That even she could remember
what he was wearing

01:45.441 --> 01:46.407
or what he looked like,

01:46.409 --> 01:47.775
she wouldn't tell you.

01:47.777 --> 01:49.126
She thinks all cops
are corrupt.

01:49.128 --> 01:51.829
That helping you might
bring her bad luck.

01:51.831 --> 01:53.748
Well, you tell her for me
that it is a pleasure

01:53.750 --> 01:56.717
dealing with such an upstanding
member of society.

01:59.639 --> 02:01.088
Whoa.

02:02.057 --> 02:04.141
Any luck?
She's not cooperating.

02:04.143 --> 02:06.811
Ah, she doesn't trust cops.

02:06.813 --> 02:08.461
Anyhow.

02:08.464 --> 02:09.930
Guy's laying down,
mid-massage,

02:09.931 --> 02:11.965
shooter busts in the door,
starts blasting,

02:11.967 --> 02:13.100
turns around, walks away.

02:13.102 --> 02:15.152
What do we know
about the victim?

02:15.154 --> 02:17.855
Uh, the victim is
Michael Reade, 32;

02:17.857 --> 02:19.523
he owns a car
dealership in Queens.

02:19.525 --> 02:21.492
Three shots-- one to
the side, two in the back.

02:21.494 --> 02:23.360
Does he have a history?

02:23.362 --> 02:25.763
Yeah, he was busted for
possession five years ago,

02:25.765 --> 02:28.165
but he skated because the
ADA made a deal with him

02:28.167 --> 02:30.701
in exchange for testifying
against some heavy hitters.

02:31.870 --> 02:33.921
Who'd you speak to
in the D.A.'s office?

02:33.923 --> 02:35.206
My sister.

02:35.208 --> 02:37.374
Is there any aspect
of public service

02:37.376 --> 02:39.326
you Reagans are
not involved in?

02:39.328 --> 02:41.762
Politics.
Too many crooks in that.

02:50.639 --> 02:51.856
Morning.

03:13.211 --> 03:15.162
What?
Move.

03:15.164 --> 03:16.213
What do you mean, move?

03:16.215 --> 03:18.465
Hey, that's my money, punk!

03:18.467 --> 03:22.469
I will shoot your ass.

03:41.106 --> 03:42.439
Come on.

03:48.914 --> 03:51.115
Our numbers are down
across the board,

03:51.117 --> 03:53.500
except for grand larceny
of cell phones.

03:53.502 --> 03:55.119
That's going backwards.

03:55.121 --> 03:56.670
Commissioner?

03:58.623 --> 04:01.508
I want a new strategy...
Excuse me.

04:02.260 --> 04:04.345
And I want it on my desk

04:04.347 --> 04:07.131
by the end of the day.

04:08.516 --> 04:13.086
There's only a few people
who can walk into this office

04:13.088 --> 04:15.940
unannounced, at will.

04:15.942 --> 04:18.425
Could it be you're starting
to take advantage of that?

04:30.155 --> 04:32.489
What's wrong?

04:34.133 --> 04:38.133
